text:
Church of Christ welcomes everybody who wants to know more about Jesus and God!
Every Sunday
English Worship: 9am
Chinese Worship: 9:30am

North-east church of Christ meets here at 3pm.

Beautiful, quaint building with a backyard with mango and banana trees. Wheelchair accessible except for level 2.

I was a member there since and I misses all the brothers and sister there I always wanted to make a come back but was somehow got a step back circumstances occurred. Hence, please pray for me that this coming Sunday to come and visit the church on (15th July 18). I really miss all if you and especially God. My contact is 93381330 Alan
